    { "id": "ko_jh_058", "levels": [{ "front": "To like / To enjoy", "back": "좋아하다 / 즐기다", "romanized": "joahada / jeulgida", "grammarNote": "'좋아하다' (joahada) = to like. Pattern: 'X를/을 좋아해요' (X-reul/eul joahaeyo, I like X). For activities: 'X하는 걸 좋아해요' (X haneun geol joahaeyo, I like doing X). '즐기다' (jeulgida) = to enjoy (stronger enjoyment)." }, { "front": "I like reading. She likes singing.", "back": "독서를 좋아해요. 그녀는 노래를 좋아해요.", "romanized": "dokseoreul joahaeyo. geunyeoneun noraereul joahaeyo" }] },
